<dl id="n01077a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n01" href="#n01077a">N01 (VI.B.10)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n01all.htm#n01077a"> 77(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ for 1 armed men</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[EXECUTIONER&apos;S DEATH]</font> Henry Albert Pierrepoint, for 11 years chief public executioner of England <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> died yesterday morning at his home <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> <font color="green">[F]</font>ollowing the hanging of <mark>a one-armed man</mark> in 1908 he invented a strap that has since been used for the pinioning of one-armed persons condemned to capitol punishment. <small> <a name="DM15dec22" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#DM15dec22"><cite title="source">Daily Mail</cite></a> (15 December 1922) 7/2</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
